data.description: Welcome home to 378 Highland Falls Dr in Hiram, GA! Experience the ease and comfort of one-level living in this charming ranch-style abode. Boasting spacious 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home offers a cozy retreat with ample room to relax and unwind. Step inside to discover a well-maintained interior adorned with low-maintenance luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout. Recently painted walls create a fresh and inviting atmosphere, while newer roof and appliances ensure peace of mind for years to come. Enjoy the open layout and gas fireplace.  Experience ultimate relaxation in the screened porch just off the primary suite, perfect for sipping your morning coffee or unwinding after a long day. Step outside to your fenced yard, providing privacy and security for outdoor enjoyment. Discover versatility in the large bonus area, offering endless possibilities for use as a sunroom, office, or whatever your heart desires. This community offers an array of amenities, including a clubhouse, playground, pool, and fitness center. Say goodbye to yard work with front yard maintenance included. Don't miss your chance to call 378 Highland Falls Dr home sweet home! Schedule your showing today and embrace the lifestyle of convenience and comfort this property has to offer.
